226
00:12:06,158 --> 00:12:08,525
<i>[ father: ] tell her we'll have</i>         

227
00:12:08,627 --> 00:12:17,235
<i>an answer for her tomorrow.</i>       

228
00:12:17,335 --> 00:12:20,071
