920
00:58:51,594 --> 00:58:54,863
[ screaming ]         

921
00:58:54,964 --> 00:59:07,642
<i>[ sirens continue ]</i>      

922
00:59:07,743 --> 00:59:11,079
 [ Alan: ] if I don't turn out the light,  
