923
00:59:11,180 --> 00:59:13,048
[ speaking French ]             

924
00:59:14,183 --> 00:59:15,650
<i>[ Alan: ] Naomi,</i>             
<i>listen to the radio.</i>     

925
00:59:15,751 --> 00:59:16,517
Hello, America.        

926
00:59:16,619 --> 00:59:18,086
Yes, it's true --        

927
