933
00:59:39,341 --> 00:59:41,843
Naomi, hey.             

934
00:59:41,944 --> 00:59:43,845
<i>You don't have to be afraid.</i>         

935
00:59:43,946 --> 00:59:47,949
<i>[ monster: ]</i>         
<i>and now for some headlights</i>     
<i>with salt and pepper!</i>     

936
00:59:48,050 --> 00:59:51,886
<i>And I love your street lights!</i>      

937
00:59:51,988 --> 00:59:54,322
<i>Oh, they're like lollipops.</i>        

938
00:59:54,423 --> 00:59:56,324
Cherry lollipops!       

939
00:59:56,425 --> 00:59:57,626
<i>Lemon lollipops!</i>       

940
00:59:57,727 --> 00:59:59,293
<i>And lime lollipops!</i>      

941
00:59:59,394 --> 01:00:02,831
<i>[ laughing ]</i>         

942
01:00:02,932 --> 01:00:07,168
[ sirens ]              

943
01:00:07,269 --> 01:00:13,307
<i>[ monster: ] oh, I think I'm</i>               
