De couer.           

1130
01:12:45,727 --> 01:12:46,994
Ami de couer.         

1131
01:12:47,095 --> 01:12:49,062
Ami de coe.                     

1132
01:12:49,163 --> 01:12:52,132
Couer.             

1133
01:12:52,233 --> 01:12:53,934
